OL,3,C'Serious' breach triggers police probe
OL,4,Cinto Tamworth election
OL,6,FA 'serious' breach of electoral law
OL,7,Fhas triggered police involvement in
OL,8,FTamworth.
OL,10,FIt is alleged that before the results
OL,11,Fwere formally declared, a post was
OL,12,Fshared on social media, revealing the
OL,13,Foutcome of the election.
OL,15,FThe election in nine wards took place
OL,16,Flast week, and saw Reform UK win all
OL,17,Fnine seats, while Labour lost a
OL,18,Fmajority on the council, which fell
OL,19,Finto no overall control.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
