OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778674272
OL,3,C'Serious' breach triggers police probe
OL,4,Cinto Tamworth election
OL,6,FThe since-deleted post on Wilnecote
OL,7,FReform ` Stonydelph/Quarry Hill/
OL,8,FHockley Facebook page shared that
OL,9,FReform UK had won all nine seats.
OL,11,FStephen Gabriel, Tamworth Borough
OL,12,FCouncil Returning Officer confirmed:
OL,13,F"We were made aware that the outcome
OL,14,Fof the Tamworth local election was
OL,15,Fposted on the Wilnecote Reform `
OL,16,FStonydelph/Quarry Hill/Hockley
OL,17,FFacebook page before being confirmed
OL,18,For announced.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
