PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778674272
OL,3,C'Serious' breach triggers police probe
OL,4,Cinto Tamworth election
OL,6,F"Section 66 of the Representation of
OL,7,Fthe People Act 1983 outlines the
OL,8,Fsecrecy requirements of the count. If
OL,9,Ffound guilty of an offence a fine or a
OL,10,Fprison sentence of six months could be
OL,11,Fordered."
OL,13,FHe continued: "We took immediate
OL,14,Faction and called the current Reform
OL,15,Fcouncillor forward to discuss, ask for
OL,16,Fthe post to be removed and reminded of
OL,17,Fthe secrecy requirements of the count.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
