PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778674272
OL,3,C'Serious' breach triggers police probe
OL,4,Cinto Tamworth election
OL,6,F"This is a very serious issue, and it
OL,7,Fwas made clear that we will report to
OL,8,Fthe Single Point of Contact at
OL,9,FStaffordshire Police."
OL,11,FStaffordshire Police spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "We're aware of reports
OL,13,Finvolving the early publishing of
OL,14,Finformation relating to the result of
OL,15,Fthe Tamworth Borough Council local
OL,16,Felection today (Friday 8 May).
OL,18,F"We are continuing to liaise with the
OL,19,Flocal authority and the Electoral
OL,20,FCommission as part of our enquiries."
OL,26,@qD@VO]tD@GOUzD@AOU|D@eO]
